data.description: Beautiful brick 1-level offering 3BR/2BA + bonus room on large .7 acre lot in lovely Magnolia Downs. Gleaming hardwood flooring in living room, kitchen, breakfast and hallway. Huge (16' x 30') new deck, HVAC and water heater. Kitchen offers an abundance of solid oak cabinets, solid surface countertops and stainless appliances. Split bedroom plan features master with separate jetted tub and shower, dual vanities and spacious walk-in closet. Bonus/rec room in basement plus 2-car garage and tons of storage. Don't miss this amazing opportunity!
